overview.en: Bade is a kind of virtual financial asset. Its design purpose is to token RMB on the blockchain. Its value is bound to the value of its collateral. At the same time, bade is not a company in the traditional sense. It has taken a key step in the evolution of digital asset trading platform to the community. Bade community is an open, transparent and token organization. Bade represents the legitimate rights and interests of bade business alliance. Bade business is applied to multi ecosystem.
overview.zh: BADE是一种虚拟金融资产，其设计目的是在区块链上代币化的人民币，它的价值与其抵押品的价值绑定.同时，BADE不是传统意义的公司，它迈出了数字资产交易平台向社区进化的关键一步。BADE社区是一个公开透明的、token化的组织BADE代表 BADE商业联盟的合法权益，BADE商业应用于多生态体系。
